# Goal: start N-sample calibration collection (see
# CalibrationBroadcasterConfig::num_samples for the default N — this is
# empty for now since overriding N per-call isn't needed yet, matching the
# project's convention of tuning via YAML params, not per-call args).
---
# Result: final status once collection finishes (success) or is aborted.
# The computed transform itself is not duplicated here — it's already
# broadcast on /tf by calibration_broadcaster_node; read it from there.
bool success
string message
float64 max_spread_deg
float64 mean_spread_deg
---
# Feedback: published after each accepted sample.
uint32 samples_collected
uint32 samples_total